{
  "stem": "58.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like you saw it happened in Germany, at Kristallnacht and all the-- you see, so-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] All the European countries as I see them now that if you were born there and lived-- Jews lived in Grojec since the 1700s, if I'm not mistaken.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have an article here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have a Jewish encyclopedia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But still they don't consider you-- in the first couple hundred years, you didn't have any rights, until about 1850 or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they gave people rights to own land and businesses and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you always felt a stranger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A matter of fact, I feel a stranger wherever I go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it's, it's in you, when you went through what I went through, it's-- wherever you go, unless you go to Israel, I feel, I feel free.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I feel like I belong, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's no, it's no hiding that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's the honest truth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, everybody thought that it, it will pass.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because people weren't used to-- it used to be free, you were on the market to sell stuff, nobody bothered you, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then a couple years before the war, it start really getting pesty, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was not involved in the market to sell, so I didn't feel the-- but I saw it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I didn't feel the way the people felt when they had to sell merchandise, you see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then it's-- it was all till the war came around and the real mess came, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the, the German declared war, it took him only a few days [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to come to our city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First the city was bombed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The boat, the flour mills were taken out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
